---
const features = [
  {
    title: 'Puente OIDC / OAuth 2.0',
    description:
      'Conectamos tu aplicación legacy a un Identity Provider moderno mediante OIDC y OAuth 2.0, forzando MFA (TOTP / Push) o biometría para generar una sesión válida.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101
           m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-green to-bn-teal',
  },
  {
    title: 'Conector On-Prem',
    description:
      'Un conector liviano (WAR) que se despliega en tu servidor JDE, SAP o PeopleSoft. Sin cambios en tu infraestructura, sin exponer credenciales locales.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2
           M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2
           m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-teal to-bn-teal-light',
  },
  {
    title: 'Autenticación Federada',
    description:
      'Habilita login corporativo con Microsoft Azure AD o Google Workspace. Los usuarios usan su cuenta de correo existente — sin contraseñas locales adicionales.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945
           M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0
           2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064
           M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-lime to-bn-green',
  },
  {
    title: 'Multi-Tenant & Multi-Instance',
    description:
      'Un único backend SaaS sirve múltiples organizaciones y múltiples instancias de JDE. Enrutamiento inteligente basado en host y prefijo de ruta.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2
           m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2
           M7 7h10"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-teal to-bn-green',
  },
  {
    title: 'Zero-Trust Security',
    description:
      'Tokens de corta vida (TTL ~60s), validación RS256 vía JWKS remoto, servicio central anti-replay (JTI + Redis), allowlist de Return URLs y mapping de identidades.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944
           a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622
           5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-navy to-bn-teal',
  },
  {
    title: 'Auditoría Completa',
    description:
      'Cada evento de autenticación queda registrado con correlation ID, tenant, instancia, usuario y resultado. Trazabilidad total para cumplimiento y forensics.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"
        d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2
           M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2
           m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/>
    </svg>`,
    accent: 'from-bn-green to-bn-lime',
  },
];
---

<section id="que-somos" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block bg-bn-teal text-white text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5">
        ¿Qué Somos?
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-bn-navy leading-tight">
        El puente entre tus sistemas legacy<br/>y la autenticación moderna
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-bn-navy/55 leading-relaxed">
        Bridnext no reemplaza tu aplicación — la conecta. Implementa SSO y MFA en JDE, SAP o PeopleSoft
        en semanas, no meses, sin tocar tu lógica de negocio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {features.map((f, i) => (
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-bn-navy/8 p-7 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-bn-navy/8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          style={`animation-delay: ${i * 80}ms`}
        >
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class={`inline-flex items-center justify-center w-13 h-13 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br ${f.accent} text-white mb-5 p-2.5`}>
            <Fragment set:html={f.icon} />
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-bn-navy mb-2.5 group-hover:text-bn-teal transition-colors">
            {f.title}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-bn-navy/55 leading-relaxed">
            {f.description}
          </p>

          <!-- Accent line on hover -->
          <div class={`absolute bottom-0 left-7 right-7 h-0.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r ${f.accent} scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300`}></div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
